OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774703465
OL,3,CDouble murderer given whole life order
OL,4,Cafter sentence ruled too lenient
OL,6,FA man who stabbed his pregnant
OL,7,Fgirlfriend to death, while on licence
OL,8,Ffor an earlier murder, has been handed
OL,9,Fa whole life order after judges at the
OL,10,FCourt of Appeal ruled his sentence was
OL,11,F"unduly lenient".
OL,13,FShaine March was jailed for life with
OL,14,Fa minimum term of 42 years last
OL,15,FOctober for the murder of Alana
OL,16,FOdysseos.
OL,18,FHe stabbed and slashed her 23 times at
OL,19,Fher home in Walthamstow in July 2024.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
